<https://deckstats.net/decks/search/?search_cards_commander[]=Sarkhan+the+Masterless&search_cards_commander[]=Volt+Charge&search_format=17> (where either of the commander/signature spell can be first)

<https://deckstats.net/decks/search/?search_cards_commander[]=Feather%2C> the Redeemed&search_format=10"
